        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "Data entry panels allow you to specify information such as data set"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "names, or operating system commands.  The fields in which you may enter"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "information are labeled and preceded with an arrow.  If you do not enter"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "a required value or if you enter inconsistent values, you will be"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "prompted with a message."
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "┌"
      },
      {
        "type": "field_row",
        "fields": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "content": "The example at the right    │"
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "content": "SPF/PC(1)  BROWSE  ENTRY PANEL"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "field_row",
        "fields": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "content": "shows part of the browse    │"
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "content": "COMMAND"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
